and he goes after it...

233
00:15:22,027 --> 00:15:24,325
and he digs in.

234
00:15:28,601 --> 00:15:31,126
Hi. How are you?

235
00:15:31,203 --> 00:15:33,501
Marlee, this is Bonnie Sherow.

236
00:15:33,572 --> 00:15:36,370
She read Tales of Fury.

237
00:15:37,476 --> 00:15:40,536
l loved it.
l thought it was wonderful.

238
00:15:40,613 --> 00:15:44,447
l think you're perfect for Ariel.
You're perfect for the part.

239
00:15:45,784 --> 00:15:48,685
We're going to make a couple changes
in the third act.

240
00:15:48,754 --> 00:15:50,745
You should set up a meeting.

241
00:15:52,424 --> 00:15:54,358
Yeah, sure.

242
00:15:54,426 --> 00:15:56,417
