-You're the last one to believe.

285
00:18:23,509 --> 00:18:25,306
Am l out?

286
00:18:25,377 --> 00:18:28,403
You're not out, but you'd better
start thinking about a roommate.

287
00:18:28,480 --> 00:18:31,881
Relax, you can handle this.
You can make it work for you.

288
00:18:31,950 --> 00:18:35,750
- Larry?
- Dick. Sorry to crash your party.

289
00:18:35,821 --> 00:18:39,518
- Do you know everybody?
- l will before the night's out.

290
00:18:39,591 --> 00:18:41,616
You will, indeed.

291
00:18:44,463 --> 00:18:48,126
- Great party, Dick.
- Good. Did you get some food?

292
