Listen to this.

293
00:18:55,107 --> 00:18:57,905
'He lifts her dress.
She kisses him harder.

294
00:18:57,976 --> 00:19:01,776
He puts his hands in her underpants.
She grabs his shoulders.

295
00:19:01,847 --> 00:19:06,614
He pulls her dress above her waist.
